Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

{
	"id": 1,
    "username": "omar1234",
    "passwordHash": "hashed_password",
    "fullName": "Omar Doe",
    "email": "john.1e@example.com",
    "phone": "1234567890",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "createdAt": "2026-04-02T10:33:00Z",
    "createdBy": 1,
    "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T10:33:00Z",
    "updatedBy": 1,
    "deletedAt": null
}

### Get BY ID
GET  {{base}}/user/4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

###Get ALL USER
GET  {{base}}/user?page=1&limit=10&total=0
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8	


